downloadTitle: Microsoft BizTalk Adapters 2010 for Enterprise Applications Installation Guide
downloadDescription: Installation guide for Microsoft BizTalk Adapters 2010 for Enterprise Applications.
detailsSection: The installation guide explains how to install Microsoft BizTalk Adapters 2010 for Enterprise Applications.
systemRequirementsSection: For HTM files: Microsoft Internet Explorer or other HTML viewer
installInstructionSection:
1. Click the Download button to start the download.

  2. Do one of the following:
    • To start the installation immediately, click Open.
    • To copy the download to your computer for installation at a later time, click Save.
    • To cancel the installation, click Cancel.
